The present book is a must-have for all undergraduate medical students as it prepares them for both theory and viva-voce examinations. It would also be useful to paramedical, dental, homeopathy and ayurveda students, besides those preparing for PG entrance examinations.

Simply written, revised and updated text, arranged topic-wise for clarity and easy comprehension.
Covers entire syllabus of physiology laid down by the Medical Council of India and various medical universities.
Question-Answer format for quick revision of the whole course.
Large number of line diagrams, flowcharts and tables.
